        "subject": "LU-18141 mgs: don't check for NULL before free'ing",
        "message": "LU-18141 mgs: don't check for NULL before free'ing\n\nThe common free'ing macros already check for NULL,\nso we don't need to explicitly check this beforehand.\n\nThe patch has been generated with the coccinelle script below.\n\n@@\nexpression E;\n@@\n- if (E != NULL)\n(\n  OBD_FREE_PTR(E);\n|\n  OBD_FREE(E, ...);\n|\n  LIBCFS_FREE(E, ...);\n|\n  CFS_FREE_PTR(E);\n|\n  CFS_FREE_PTR_ARRAY(E, ...);\n)\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Timothy Day <timday@amazon.com>\nChange-Id: Ie6ae568738264444be9703e856254a0470e85f7b\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
